rows.name:
I started up my dancing again.
Not full time or anything, but
in between my other work.

rows.label: tlk45450111_06_msg0002
rows.name:
What I really want is to
become better than Harghal.

rows.label: tlk45450111_06_msg0003
rows.name:
I want to be able to impress her
when we meet again someday!

rows.label: tlk45450111_06_msg0004
rows.name:
It feels like I'm really starting
to get my life back into gear
again thanks to you guys.
